### Get all flowers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flower

### Get flower by type
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flower/type/ROSE

### Get flower by type - TULIP
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flower/type/TULIP

### Create a new flower (description auto-generated from type)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flower
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ROSE",
  "color": "RED",
  "sepalLength": 2.5,
  "price": 12.99
}

### Create another flower
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flower
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "TULIP",
  "color": "YELLOW",
  "sepalLength": 1.8,
  "price": 8.50
}

### Create a cactus
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flower
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "CACTUS",
  "color": "GREEN",
  "sepalLength": 0.5,
  "price": 5.50
}

### List delivery methods
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/delivery

### Simulate delivery - DHL
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/delivery/simulate?method=dhl&itemType=ROSE

### Simulate delivery - Post
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/delivery/simulate?method=post&itemType=TULIP

### List payment methods
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payment

### Simulate payment - Credit Card
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payment/simulate?method=credit-card&amount=100

### Simulate payment - PayPal
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payment/simulate?method=paypal&amount=50.75

### Create a white romashka
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flower
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ROMASHKA",
  "color": "WHITE",
  "sepalLength": 1.0,
  "price": 3.50
}

### Create a blue tulip
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/flower
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "TULIP",
  "color": "BLUE",
  "sepalLength": 2.0,
  "price": 7.00
}

### Create an order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": ["ROSE", "TULIP"],
  "payment": "credit-card",
  "delivery": "dhl"
}

### Create another order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": ["ROMASHKA", "CACTUS"],
  "payment": "paypal",
  "delivery": "post"
}
